Version: 1.1.7
Release: alt12

Summary: xvidcap is a screen capture tool
Group: Video
License: GPL

Url: http://sourceforge.net/projects/xvidcap/
Source: http://prdownloads.sourceforge.net/%name/%name-%version.tar.gz
